description: Father Jim Byrne was a mentor and family friend.  He spent his later years sharing Christ message to the Holy Cross and Immaculate Heart neighborhoods, to name a few. By serving a totally different pizza and using top quality ingredients, we give tribute to Father Jim Byrne. Enjoy!!!While we spend our weekends at Flat12 Bierwerks, we are an independent mobile kitchen that will travel to your location, by appointment.
name: Byrnes Pizza
